Package tds

Task data structure (TDS) containing all the classes for storing and manipulating task object.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Attributes
    A list of constants used to identify a specify attribute type.
    Task
    A task object used to store task name, time and different attributes.
    TaskTree
    Provides methods for storing and manipulating Task via TreeSet.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    Attributes.TYPE
    Attribute type constants used for attributes identification
    Task.FLAG_TYPE
    Field value constant for flag attribute.
    Task.PRIORITY_TYPE
    Field value constant for priority attribute.
